OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,FLiverpool FC are set to open formal
OL,7,Ftalks with Andoni Iraola in the coming
OL,8,Fdays as they seek to make a swift
OL,9,Fappointment to replace Arne Slot.
OL,11,FThe Dutchman was sacked on Saturday,
OL,12,F30 May, just 12 months on from winning
OL,13,Fonly the club's second Premier League
OL,14,Ftitle in 30 years after a pitiful
OL,15,Fdefence ended with them stumbling to a
OL,16,Ffifth-placed finish.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
