OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780387618
OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,FAfter a review of the campaign, beset
OL,7,Ffirst by the death of Diogo Jota and
OL,8,Fthen a series of injuries which
OL,9,Fhampered the team's performance to the
OL,10,Fextent they lost 19 matches, owners
OL,11,FFenway Sports Group decided a change
OL,12,Fof direction was needed.
OL,14,FIraola, who is leaving Bournemouth
OL,15,Fafter guiding them to their highest
OL,16,Fleague finish of sixth, securing a
OL,17,Fmaiden European campaign, was
OL,18,Fidentified as a front-runner and it is
OL,19,Funderstood an official approach will
OL,20,Fbe made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780387618
OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,FLiverpool's sporting director Richard
OL,7,FHughes already has a relationship with
OL,8,Fthe Spaniard, having appointed him at
OL,9,FBournemouth when he was in a similar
OL,10,Frole there.
OL,12,FIt is understood Iraola, who is said
OL,13,Fto be keen on taking the job, has
OL,14,Falready spoken to Crystal Palace,
OL,15,FBayer Leverkusen and AC Milan.
OL,17,FThe decision to remove Slot was a
OL,18,Fswift one because as late as Friday
OL,19,Fevening he still believed he would be
OL,20,Fcontinuing next season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
