OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,FPosting a picture of him with his arm
OL,7,Faround his fellow Dutchman, captain
OL,8,FVirgil van Dijk wrote on Instagram:
OL,9,F"We'll never forget winning the
OL,10,FPremier League in our first season
OL,11,Ftogether.
OL,13,F"Thank you, Trainer, and best of luck
OL,14,Fto you and your family for the future."
OL,16,FMac Allister wrote: "I'll always be
OL,17,Fgrateful for the time we spent
OL,18,Ftogether. Winning a Premier League is
OL,19,Fnot easy and you were a big part of
OL,20,Fthat success. Thank you and wish you
OL,21,Fall the best."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@gO]xD@UOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
