OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780387618
OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,FJones, whose unhappiness at not
OL,7,Fstarting regularly has seen him linked
OL,8,Fwith Inter Milan, said: "Thank you and
OL,9,Fall the best for the future. Respect
OL,10,Fyou as a man for what you gave our
OL,11,Fclub."
OL,13,FLiverpool have also confirmed Van
OL,14,FDijk's central defensive partner
OL,15,FIbrahima Konate will leave the club
OL,16,Fwhen his contract expires next month
OL,17,Fafter failing to come to an agreement
OL,18,Fover financial terms for a new deal.
OL,20,F"Representing this club has been an
OL,21,Fhonour," Konate posted on Instagram.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@FO]|D@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
