OL,3,CLiverpool in talks with Andoni Iraola
OL,4,Cas they look to replace Slot
OL,6,F"We've shared incredible moments
OL,7,Ftogether...highs and lows, trophies,
OL,8,Fchallenges, lifelong friendships, and
OL,9,Fheartbreaking moments that will stay
OL,10,Fwith us forever, none more painful
OL,11,Fthan losing our brother Diogo.
OL,13,F"Losing my father this year was one of
OL,14,Fthe hardest periods of my life, but
OL,15,Feven through hardship, my commitment
OL,16,Fto this club never changed. During the
OL,17,Ftoughest moments, I gave everything I
OL,18,Fhad for this badge."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
